      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VALLEY STAR NZ (5) is a newcomer to the Jonah Hutchinson yard and brings strong form from NSW where has has put together a string of good efforts at Menangle including a last-start win from a 40m handicap. Placed in a trial here. Can measure up. NELLIE JOY (1) drew wider last start but won three in a row at Albion Park prior, one of them from this barrier when she led and kept going. Could be hard to catch. KODA DA MODA (8) is racing well having only once missed the top-three in her last five starts, coming from this barrier for second at Albion Park last time. Genuine threat. DARCYS FIREBALL (7) has placed in three of his last four starts and has recorded a win and a placing in two tries at this longer distance.",
